Hi. This is my first addon. Automatic UVProjection is oriented to create a fast Camera Mapping projects.
It is not perfect, but it facilitates and improves very much the camera mapping technique in blender.
If someone wants to modify it or to improve it he can share it with us in http://zebus.xtreemhost.com/pyblend/

